briefTitle: A Multi-Center, Randomized, Open-Label Study to Assess the Immunogenicity and Safety of Denosumab in Pre-filled Syringe Compared to Vial in Subjects With Low Bone Mineral Density
officialTitle: A Multi-Center, Randomized, Open-Label Study to Assess the Immunogenicity and Safety of Denosumab in Pre-filled Syringe Compared to Vial in Subjects With Low Bone Mineral Density
summary: The purpose of this study is to compare the immunogenicity profiles of denosumab pre-filled syringe (PFS) and vial at 6 months in postmenopausal women with low bone mineral density (BMD).

primaryOutcome.measure: Number of Participants Who Tested Positive for Anti-denosumab Antibodies at Month 6
